sheep-wash tobacco
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a tobacco of a grade only suitable for dipping sheep against scab and other diseases.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
