Quote: If a more equable scale of duties could be introduced, he should feel inclined to recommend that Sheep-Wash Tobacco should be taken from the free list .. the Sheep-farmer would willingly pay a moderate duty on Sheep-Wash Tobacco if duties were lowered on Tea and Sugars ...
