Date: 24/1/1893
Source: Marlborough Express
Author:
Vol / Page: 2
Edition:
Quote: The first item is boiling water, then add spirits of wine, a chunk of President tobacco - any other will do so long as it is not sheep wash tobacco - Perry Davis Pain Killer to taste, with a flourish of white sugar, mix well with an axe handle, strain, bottle, and use in forty-eight hours. This is a powerful stimulant capable of burning the bowels out of a cast iron dog.
